casebody.data:
Office of Disciplinary Counsel v. Michaels.

[Cite as Disciplinary Counsel v. Michaels (1990), 50 Ohio St. 3d 607.]

(No. D.D. 87-34 Submitted March 28, 1990 Decided April 11, 1990.)

The application for reinstatement to the practice of law is granted. William P. Michaels is reinstated to the practice of law in the state of Ohio.

(For earlier case, see [1988], 38 Ohio St. 3d 248, 527 N.E. 2d 299.)

Moyer, C.J., Sweeney, Holmes, Douglas, Wright, H. Brown and Resnick, JJ., concur,
